---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Hyperformance Media"
  description="How Hyperformance Media collects, uses, and protects your personal information and data."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <section class="bg-background px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-h2 text-text-primary" data-reveal>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-body-sm text-text-secondary" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Hyperformance Media collects information you voluntarily provide when you contact us, request a consultation, or engage our services. This may include your name, email address, phone number, company name, and details about your project requirements. We also collect basic analytics data (pages visited, time on site) through standard server logs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            We use the information you provide to respond to inquiries, deliver services, send project updates, and improve our website and offerings. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Your information is stored securely and access is restricted to authorized team members. We use industry-standard practices to protect your data, including encrypted communication channels and secure password management. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">4. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Our website does not use tracking cookies for advertising purposes. We may use essential cookies for site functionality if implemented in the future. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            In the course of delivering services, we may use third-party tools (such as Google Analytics, Google Search Console, or social media platforms) with your permission. These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information held by Hyperformance Media. To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at the email or phone number below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            We retain client information for the duration of our engagement and for a reasonable period thereafter for record-keeping and legal compliance. You may request deletion of your data at any time, subject to ongoing contractual obligations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            For privacy-related questions or requests, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@hyperformancemedia.in" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">info@hyperformancemedia.in</a> or +91-9643534849.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
